
Graph Coloring (GC)

Compile:

    make            # Baseline CDP version
    make all        # All versions
    make test       # Test compiled versions
    make test-all   # Compile all versions and test them

Run:

    ./gc.<version>
    ./gc.<version> -h   # Help

Source: A. V. P. Grosset, P. Zhu, S. Liu, S. Venkatasubramanian, and M. Hall. “Evaluating graph coloring on GPUs.” In Proceedings of the 16th ACM Symposium on Principles and Practice of Parallel Programming, PPoPP'11, pp. 297–298, ACM, 2011.

